---
---
<section class="philosophy reveal" id="philosophy">
  <div class="philosophy__inner">
    <span class="eyebrow philosophy__eyebrow">Our Philosophy</span>
    <blockquote class="philosophy__quote">
      <p>"We built this place for people who need the forest to slow them down.
      No TVs in the rooms. No conference calls in the garden.
      Just the Pacific Northwest, doing what it does best."</p>
    </blockquote>
    <p class="philosophy__attribution">— The MacLeod Family, Owners</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .philosophy {
    background: var(--forest);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-lg);
  }

  .philosophy__inner {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .philosophy__eyebrow {
    color: var(--amber);
  }

  .philosophy__quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.35;
    max-width: 28ch;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--amber);
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  }

  .philosophy__quote:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .philosophy__quote p {
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .philosophy__attribution {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--amber);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
</style>
